<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, June 1 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange index
closed at 1,567.4 points Tuesday, up 5.9 points from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 13.23 million Kuwaiti dinars (43.65 million
U.S. dollars) as 81.13 million shares were traded in 1,645
deals. 
