for some 70 days and has brought serious tragedy to the Yugoslav
people. This is simple hegemony and power politics, he said,
adding that U.S.-led NATO's attack on the Chinese embassy is a
wantonly trampling on Chinese sovereignty and that China requires
them to give a full explanation.
</P>
<P>
China needs to speed up its military modernization, he said,
because it will contribute to Chinese sovereignty, national
security, and social stability. 
