<HEADLINE> Citibank Now Doing RMB Business in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 1 (Xinhua) -- Citibank operating here has got
authorization to deal in renminbi as of today in Shenzhen, making
it the first American bank to do business in renminbi in the two
cities, the most robust financial markets in China.
</P>
<P>
