<HEADLINE> Results of First AVC Cup Men's Club Volleyball </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, Anhui, June 2 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results of
the first AVC Cup Men's Club Volleyball Tournament here on the
opening day:
</P>
<P>
Samsung Fire &AMP; Marine Insurance, South Korea, bt Paykan, Iran,
25-20, 25-17, 25-20
</P>
<P>
Sichuan Fo Lan, China, bt NEC Blue Rockets, Japan, 25-22, 25-20,
23-25, 25-21
</P>
<P>
Chendu Army, China, bt Al Rayan, Qatar, 25-22, 25-11, 25-18.
</P>
