Visitors from east China's Jiangsu and Zhejiang provinces and
Shanghai City and from countries and regions including Japan, the
Republic of Korea, Britain, Germany, Hong Kong and Taiwan, also
attended trade talks which have helped attract 23.3 million US
dollars of investment to the province.
