consular conventions and other inter-government agreements,
including reciprocal visits of citizens and visa-free treatment
for tourist groups, agreement on the cooperation of utilization
and development of forest resources, an agreement to continue
cooperating in the energy sector, and one covering regulations for
temporary laborers between the two countries.
