<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, June 1 (Xinhua) -- Andre Agassi of the United States
entered the semifinals of the French Open after beating Marcelo
Filippini of Uruguay in straight sets here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Agassi barely broke a sweat in winning the match 6-2, 6-2, 6-0
in just 72 minutes.
</P>
<P>
